12 issues found and fixed, commit staged. Summary of what was resolved:

- **tsconfig.json** — created (was missing entirely)
- **Prisma 7 compat** — removed `url` from datasource, added `prisma.config.ts` + `@prisma/adapter-pg`
- **Schema enum** — `subscriptionStatus` pointed at wrong enum (`OnboardingStatus` → `SubscriptionStatus`)
- **Stripe API version** — pinned to `2025-02-24.acacia`, lazy init to avoid build crash
- **Infisical SDK** — fixed `updateSecret`/`createSecret` call signatures
- **Mastra StepResult** — `result.outputAs` doesn't exist on `StepResult`, fixed to `(child as any).outputAs`
- **executor.ts** — implicit `any` in deps callback typed
- **Stripe webhook** — `SubscriptionStatus` type violations resolved
- **Next.js root layout** — created `src/app/layout.tsx` (required by Next 15)
- **tRPC providers** — created `src/app/providers.tsx` with proper context wrappers
- **tRPC route handler** — created `/api/trpc/[trpc]/route.ts` (all client calls were 404ing)
- **next-auth v5** — pinned to `5.0.0-beta.30` (stable v5 doesn't exist)
